name: Pink Vintage Rhinestone Sweet 15 Quinceañera Tiara in Silver 242
description:
Item Style Number: HP-242 (15) Silver Pink

This Sweet 15 Quinceañera headpiece will make every girl feel like a true princess on her special day with all of its pink majestic sparkle and luminous silver plating! This tiara features a regal design that embraces a hierarchy of completely encrusted vintage swirls along with a signature sweet 15 embellishment suspending in the center. Combs are equipped on each end of the band to secure the headpiece into the hair with stability.

Size: Decorative accent measures 10" wide x 2.75" tall.

name: Small Pageant Rhinestone Bridal Tiara HP 1774 (Gold or Silver)
description:
Item Style Number: HP 1774

Stylish and classic, this gold plated tiara features a rhinestone encrusted floral design. This versatile piece is perfect for the classic, modern, or vintage bride. The ornamented portion of the piece measures 8-1/4" wide and 1-1/2" tall, and the piece ends in two loops that allow you to fasten it in your hair with bobby pins.

Size: 8-1/4" wide and 1-1/2" tall

name: Lovely Silver Clear Swirl Rhinestone Bridal Tiara 9845
description:
Item Style Number: HP 9845

Elegant silver plated swirls weave throughout stunning clear round-cut and pear-cut rhinestones in this romantic and classic design. This is a charming piece for any classic bride and coordinates perfectly with a white or ivory wedding dress. This is also a lovely accessory for proms!

Size: 1” tall with design extending 7.5” on a 13.5” band with end loops

name: Vintage Inspired Bridal Tiara HP 7009
description:
Item Style Number: HP 7009

Stunning and vintage-inspired, this tiara shimmers with an artistic arrangement of rhinestones and swarovski crystals. Perfect for your modern or vintage wedding. The ornamented portion of the band measures 8-1/2" wide and 1-1/2" tall, and rhinestones encrust the remaining combined 5" of the band. The piece ends in two loops that allow you to fasten it in your hair with bobby pins.

Size: 8-1/2" wide and 1-1/2" tall

name: Antique Silver Clear Multi Cut Rhinestone Royal Tiara Headpiece 9958
description:
This royal tiara is absolutely glamorous. With antique silver plating encrusted with baguette and round cut rhinestones this headpiece truly shines! This is the perfect accessory for any modern or classic bride!

Size: 15 3/4" (Band Length) 12 3/4" (Design Length) 3 1/2" (Embellishment Width/Height)
